From 5am Monday 30 August to 5am Saturday 2 October 2021, work for Parramatta Light Rail will result in the closure of bus stop Market St at Church St (215018).

The alternative stop will be Saint Patrick’s Cathedral, Marist Place (215071) for the 804 and 806 towards Liverpool and the 810X towards Pemulwuy.

From 5am Monday 30 August to 5am Saturday 2 October 2021, work for Parramatta Light Rail will result in the closure of bus stop Market St at Church St (215018).

The alternative stop will be Saint Patrick’s Cathedral, Marist Place (215071) for the 804 and 806 towards Liverpool and the 810X towards Pemulwuy.
